=Bit Groups / Bitgroups=

- 1 byte id
- 1 byte buffer offset
	$00		lamps
	$40		blink buffer
- Bitgroup#01 includes all controlled lamps

=BITGROUP_TABLE:
	- WPC pointer table
	- entry:
		B0-1	^next bitgroup
		B2-n	bitgroup defiition
	- bitgroup definition:
		$FA <bitgroup elt> [...] $FA
	- bitgroup elements:
		<Lamp>							single lamp
		<Flag>							single flag
		$81 <Bitgroup> $81				Bitgroup
		$85 <from-bit> <to-bit> $85		flag or lamp range

sys_bitgroupOp_ABXY
	A	ROM page of hook routine
	B	0C(rotLeft) 0E(fill), 04(???)
	X	bitgroup + buffer offset
	Y	address of hook routine

